ore</a></p> </div> </div> </div><div class="accordion-item"> <p style="font-weight: bold;" class="accordion-header" id="agenda-heading480173"> <button aria-controls="agenda-collapse480173" aria-expanded="true" class="accordion-button collapsed js-triggerRefresh" data-bs-target="#agenda-collapse480173" data-bs-toggle="collapse" type="button"> Credit and recognition of prior learning </button> </p> <div aria-labelledby="agenda-heading480173" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionRequirements" id="agenda-collapse480173"> <div class="accordion-body"> <p>Credit for Prior Learning, also referred to as ‘Advanced Standing’ or Recognition for Prior Learning (RPL), is the process of looking at your prior study and/or experience to assess if you can be awarded academic credit or gain entry to a course on the basis of your existing knowledge and skills.</p> <p><a href="https://www.scu.edu.au/study/how-to-apply/credit-for-recognition-of-prior-learning/">Learn more</a></p> </div> </div> </div><div class="accordion-item"> <p style="font-weight: bold;" class="accordion-header" id="agenda-heading480174"> <button aria-controls="agenda-collapse480174" aria-expanded="true" class="accordion-button collapsed js-triggerRefresh" data-bs-target="#agenda-collapse480174" data-bs-toggle="collapse" type="button"> Early Offer for Year 12s </button> </p> <div aria-labelledby="agenda-heading480174" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionRequirements" id="agenda-collapse480174"> <div class="accordion-body"> <p>The Early Offer program allows Year 12 students to secure a place in a Southern Cross University undergraduate degree before Year 12 results are released. It’s designed to remove some of the pressure from Year 12 and provide a pathway directly into university study that is not based solely on Year 12 results.</p> <p><a href="https://www.scu.edu.au/study/high-school-students/entry-pathways/early-offer/">Learn more</a></p> </div> </div> </div> </di