mic credit or gain entry to a course on the basis of your existing knowledge and skills.</p> <p><a href="https://www.scu.edu.au/study/how-to-apply/credit-for-recognition-of-prior-learning/">Learn more</a></p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>',
